The concerns of the Soul are Grace and Glory;
                  Solution. 
                  holineſs here, and happineſs hereafter; a heaven here, and a heaven hereafter; a believing in Chriſt here, and a being with Chriſt hereafter; Grace here, and Glory hereafter, are undoubtedly the great concerns of the ſoul. But, to ſpeak to theſe diſtinctly.

